name: Nocturnos de México I
description: The Mexican Artisan of Artificial Intelligence is a project that seeks to reconcile a new perspective on the direction of handcrafts and traditional elements of Mexico. It looks to reflect on the position of the artisan through the use of new technologies to highlight the beauty and cultural richness of my native country. This data generates visual machine hallucinations regarding a cultural context and geographical spaces through the stylegan2 model, from which we can denote a unique futuristic aesthetic with traditional textures of Mexico.
